{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sandbox Apocalypse is a 3rd person view, open world post-apocalyptic survial game where you are responsible for your own fate. Survive in a world inhabited by zombies, gather loot, build your base and explore the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a single-developer game developed by me (Ben). The game is currently under development and available in an early access version in order to gather feedback from the community. You can clearly see which other indie and non-indie games have been an inspiration to me. My aim is to combine the survival aspect and life simulation with an extensive crafting system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is already a lot you can do whilst playing the game: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Explore the 1 by 1 kilometer (1 square kilometer map - roughly 0.4 square miles) </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight the zombies with a bunch of different weapons (and other items)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Search and find loot that will help you to survive (clothes, weapons, food, medical items) </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Salvage whatever you can within the game and build a house for yourself</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Change the environment, do some landscaping or dig trenches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Claim a vehicle and drive around </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are many things you currently cannot do or play with, but they are high on the list of priorities. I plan to add the following features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multi-player </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Day and night and weather simulation </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A map that will eventually comprise 10 x 10 kilometers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> More vehicles, weapons, loot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Modding</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Bare Knuckles","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3019830/3696ffb7a686e74589ddab4ba3e6f0792a420d2d.jpg"},{"name":"Sports Fanatic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3019830/d2ab469eefc1be2198ff56579cf99298c75c8ef8.jpg"},{"name":"Survivor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3019830/ab59743e14acb1181640dcdc429dc731588f6061.jpg"},{"name":"Bookworm","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3019830/ce3c18b0ce398db82df2f24c5c55131fe5e8f8d6.jpg"},{"name":"Scientist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3019830/8a183e43936b593bf2c9ca954092432935b40e4d.jpg"},{"name":"Death","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3019830/9f959c26632eafe6895c29ad004c09f7557d5d86.jpg"},{"name":"One Hit Kill","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3019830/73da9f37f46b49095307e70c035e05589e3a2fc9.jpg"},{"name":"Recycler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3019830/33c3a08403c00e935f4b50e5442aea6da25d43ed.jpg"},{"name":"Lumberjack","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3019830/9a0ffd0e3cfe5c45af6e38bbe37e19db1b702709.jpg"},{"name":"Woodworker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3019830/a09808d901ee8e47796eca34809028a7afba7438.jpg"}],"total":18},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019830/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732367824","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019830/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732367824","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019830/499c94c4259abaeae